&lt;h1 id="modeling-a-wealth-tax"&gt;Modeling a Wealth Tax&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;August 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some politicians are proposing to introduce wealth taxes in addition to income and capital gains taxes. Let&amp;rsquo;s try modeling the effects of various levels of wealth tax to see what they would mean in practice for a startup founder.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Suppose you start a successful startup in your twenties, and then live for another 60 years. How much of your stock will a wealth tax consume?&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>The Founder Visa</title><link>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/foundervisa/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/foundervisa/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_zh/foundervisa/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
